{"id":3287,"date":"2023-08-04T17:16:16","date_gmt":"2023-08-04T10:16:16","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/?p=3287"},"modified":"2023-08-31T14:37:46","modified_gmt":"2023-08-31T07:37:46","slug":"di-du-hoc-dai-loan-can-mang-theo-nhung-gi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/di-du-hoc-dai-loan-can-mang-theo-nhung-gi\/","title":{"rendered":"\u0110i du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan c\u1ea7n mang theo nh\u1eefng g\u00ec?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n du h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i Smart Way bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng khi chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho cu\u1ed9c h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem x\u00e9t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o. M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eeb c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n du h\u1ecdc sinh l\u00e0: &#8220;<strong>\u0110i du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan c\u1ea7n mang theo nh\u1eefng g\u00ec<\/strong>?&#8221;. \u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m du h\u1ecdc su\u00f4n s\u1ebb v\u00e0 th\u00fa v\u1ecb, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 mang \u0111i khi du h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0i Loan.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t danh s\u00e1ch chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 mang theo khi \u0111i du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t cho cu\u1ed9c h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0i Loan.<\/span><b><\/b><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\"><b>I. H\u1ed3 s\u01a1 v\u00e0 gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eadp c\u1ea3nh v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp su\u00f4n s\u1ebb t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0i Loan, \u0111i du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan c\u1ea7n mang theo nh\u1eefng g\u00ec li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd sau \u0111\u00e2y:<\/span><\/p>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>H\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfu v\u00e0 visa:<\/strong> H\u00e3y ki\u1ec3m tra xem h\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u00f2n hi\u1ec7u l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u00e3 xin visa du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc:<\/strong> \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean mang theo gi\u1ea5y m\u1eddi nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u00e0i Loan m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn v\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadp c\u1ea3nh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n:<\/strong> \u0110\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh danh t\u00ednh v\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o mang theo ch\u1ee9ng minh nh\u00e2n d\u00e2n, gi\u1ea5y khai sinh, s\u1ed5 h\u1ed9 kh\u1ea9u v\u00e0 c\u00e1c gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n kh\u00e1c c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. Khi \u0111i du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan mang theo nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft tr\u00e1nh b\u1ecb mang th\u1eeba ho\u1eb7c thi\u1ebfu.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3293\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3293\" style=\"width: 696px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3293\" src=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3-1691144133.jpg\" alt=\"ho-so-va-giay-to-can-thiet\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3-1691144133.jpg 696w, https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3-1691144133-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3293\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>H\u1ed3 s\u01a1 v\u00e0 gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>&gt;&gt; XEM TH\u00caM:<\/strong> <a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/tim-hieu-ve-xin-hoc-bong-du-hoc-dai-loan\/\">T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 xin h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng du h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00e0i loan t\u1eeb A \u0111\u1ebfn Z<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\"><b>II. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i du h\u1ecdc, h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 xem x\u00e9t \u0111i du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan c\u1ea7n mang theo nh\u1eefng g\u00ec v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh:<\/span><\/p>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng du h\u1ecdc:<\/strong> \u0110i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u00e0i Loan m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn. H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ecdc k\u1ef9 v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m n\u00e0o trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Ch\u1ee9ng minh t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh:<\/strong> \u0110\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0i Loan, h\u00e3y chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 ngu\u1ed3n thu nh\u1eadp, t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng, h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n ho\u1eb7c t\u1eeb nh\u00e0 b\u1ea3o l\u00e3nh (n\u1ebfu c\u00f3). \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 ngu\u1ed3n l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 cho chi ph\u00ed s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/di-du-hoc-dai-loan-can-bao-nhieu-tien\/\">&gt;&gt; XEM TH\u00caM: <\/a><\/strong><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/di-du-hoc-dai-loan-can-bao-nhieu-tien\/\">\u0110i du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan c\u1ea7n bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n?<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><strong><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\">III. \u0110\u1ed3 d\u00f9ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh c\u00e1c gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin quan tr\u1ecdng th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed3 d\u00f9ng c\u00e1i nh\u00e2n khi \u0111i du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan c\u1ea7n mang theo nh\u1eefng g\u00ec?\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o v\u00e0 gi\u00e0y d\u00e9p:<\/strong> Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o, gi\u00e0y d\u00e9p ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft v\u00e0 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0i Loan. H\u00e3y t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1ec1 kh\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u00e0 th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang lo\u1ea1i qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o v\u00e0 gi\u00e0y d\u00e9p ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed3 d\u00f9ng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp<\/strong>: Mang theo s\u00e1ch gi\u00e1o tr\u00ecnh, v\u1edf, b\u00fat vi\u1ebft, m\u00e1y t\u00ednh x\u00e1ch tay v\u00e0 c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp kh\u00e1c m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n cho qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0i Loan.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb di \u0111\u1ed9ng:<\/strong> Kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean mang theo \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i di \u0111\u1ed9ng, m\u00e1y t\u00ednh b\u1ea3ng, s\u1ea1c d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb di \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef li\u00ean l\u1ea1c v\u00e0 ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y. Khi \u0111i du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan c\u1ea7n mang theo nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft tr\u00e1nh b\u1ecb mang th\u1eeba ho\u1eb7c thi\u1ebfu.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3294\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3294\" style=\"width: 696px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3294\" src=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/4-1691144133.jpg\" alt=\"do-dung-ca-nhan\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/4-1691144133.jpg 696w, https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/4-1691144133-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3294\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>\u0110\u1ed3 d\u00f9ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\"><b>IV. Thu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #282828;\"><strong>Thu\u1ed1c<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">D\u00f9 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ch\u0103m s\u00f3c s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe \u1edf \u0110\u00e0i Loan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao trong khu v\u1ef1c ch\u00e2u \u00c1, vi\u1ec7c th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu th\u1ebb b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec3m y t\u1ebf ban \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c du h\u1ecdc sinh g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe y\u1ebfu. V\u00ec v\u1eady, khi chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb h\u00e0nh l\u00fd, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i thu\u1ed1c nh\u01b0 gi\u1ea3m \u0111au, h\u1ea1 s\u1ed1t, kh\u00e1ng vi khu\u1ea9n ho\u1eb7c tr\u1ecb ti\u00eau ch\u1ea3y.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n t\u1eeb mi\u1ec1n Nam, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ecbu l\u1ea1nh th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n t\u1eeb mi\u1ec1n B\u1eafc. Do \u0111\u00f3, h\u00e3y chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb d\u1ea7u c\u00f9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi kh\u00ed h\u1eadu \u0111\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0i Loan. M\u1ed7i t\u1ed1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i ng\u1ee7, h\u00e3y xoa d\u1ea7u c\u00f9 l\u00e0 v\u00e0o l\u00f2ng b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e2n \u1ea5m l\u00ean, sau \u0111\u00f3 mang t\u1ea5t. B\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 c\u1ea3m l\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7 ngon h\u01a1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u00e3y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ea7u c\u00f9 l\u00e0, v\u00ec d\u1ea7u n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee9a c\u1ed3n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m l\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m th\u00e2n nhi\u1ec7t, d\u1ec5 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3m l\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u00ec k\u1ef3 nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u xu\u00e2n khi nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1eabn kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5p (so v\u1edbi mi\u1ec1n Nam), c\u1ea3 nam v\u00e0 n\u1eef \u0111\u1ec1u n\u00ean chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t l\u1ecd vaseline \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 m\u00f4i tr\u00e1nh n\u1ee9t n\u1ebb.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3295\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3295\" style=\"width: 696px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3295\" src=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/5-1691144133.jpg\" alt=\"thuoc\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/5-1691144133.jpg 696w, https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/5-1691144133-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3295\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Thu\u1ed1c<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><strong>M\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m<\/strong><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n n\u1eef, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n mang theo qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u khi \u0111i du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan. H\u00e3y ch\u1ec9 mang nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y nh\u01b0 t\u1ea9y trang, s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m \u0110\u00e0i Loan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. T\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0i Loan, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u chu\u1ed7i si\u00eau th\u1ecb m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m nh\u01b0 POYA, Waston v\u00e0 The Cosmed, cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e3n h\u00e0ng n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 d\u00f2ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ecba nh\u01b0 Naruko, The beauty diary, Love more. Nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng thua k\u00e9m c\u00e1c m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c hay Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3296\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3296\" style=\"width: 696px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3296\" src=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/6-1691144133.jpg\" alt=\"my-pham\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/6-1691144133.jpg 696w, https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/6-1691144133-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3296\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>M\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\"><b>V. Mang theo \u201cni\u1ec1m vui\u201d v\u00e0 \u201ctinh th\u1ea7n\u201d<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110i du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan c\u1ea7n mang theo nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp \u1edf tr\u00ean th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean b\u1ecf qua vi\u1ec7c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u00e2m l\u00fd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u00e0 v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft b\u1edfi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi, con ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi v\u00e0 n\u1ebfp s\u1ed1ng m\u1edbi m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u00ednh ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 l\u1eadp l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o \u1edf \u0110\u00e0i Loan. H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c h\u1ecdc n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n t\u00ednh t\u1ef1 l\u1eadp, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. M\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0i Loan s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n khai th\u00e1c v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi h\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, du h\u1ecdc sinh c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ed3ng. B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1ng chung v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia kh\u00e1c nhau, m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi mang trong m\u00ecnh l\u1ed1i s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch ri\u00eang. Vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt c\u00e1i &#8220;t\u00f4i&#8221; v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp. H\u00e3y t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng, v\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi, tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng giao ti\u1ebfp \u0111a v\u0103n h\u00f3a.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3297\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3297\" style=\"width: 696px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3297\" src=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/7-1691144133.jpg\" alt=\"di-du-hoc-dai-loan-can-mang-theo-nhung-gi\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/7-1691144133.jpg 696w, https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/7-1691144133-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3297\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>\u0110i du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan c\u1ea7n mang theo nh\u1eefng g\u00ec<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y Smart Way \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi: &#8220;<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>\u0111i du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan c\u1ea7n mang theo nh\u1eefng g\u00ec?<\/strong>&#8220;. Mong r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u00edch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n khi \u0111i du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan c\u1ea7n mang theo nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft tr\u00e1nh b\u1ecb mang th\u1eeba ho\u1eb7c thi\u1ebfu.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ngay h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u00f9ng\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/\">Smart Way<\/a>. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n l\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00f9ng b\u1ea1n ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean h\u1ec7<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>Fanpage:\u00a0<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/duhocsmartway\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Du h\u1ecdc Smart Way<\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>Email:<\/strong>\u00a0duhocsmartway@gmail.com<\/p>\n<p><strong>Hotline:\u00a0<\/strong>0983.741.042 \u2013 0988.108.164<\/p>\n<p><strong>\u0110\u1ecba ch\u1ec9:\u00a0<\/strong>S\u1ed1 27, li\u1ec1n k\u1ec1 12, Khu \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb V\u0103n Kh\u00ea, Ph\u01b0\u1eddng La Kh\u00ea, Qu\u1eadn H\u00e0 \u0110\u00f4ng, Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n du h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i Smart Way bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng khi chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho cu\u1ed9c h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem x\u00e9t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o. M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eeb c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n du h\u1ecdc sinh l\u00e0: &#8220;\u0110i du h\u1ecdc &#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":17,"featured_media":3299,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[8],"tags":[28,30,31,29],"class_list":["post-3287","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-cam-nang-du-hoc","tag-di-du-hoc-dai-loan-can-mang-theo-nhung-gi","tag-do-dung-ca-nhan","tag-my-pham","tag-thuoc"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3287","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/17"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3287"}],"version-history":[{"count":9,"href":"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3287\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3509,"href":"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3287\/revisions\/3509"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/duhocsm